Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:48.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,手を切るくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,痛ッ!證明したい マイ存在自体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.93,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,永久ライン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.67,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,囲い込まれても セーフティライン
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.15,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,「Wanna take you high ? 」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:10.11,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,揺れる銀河 君はスマイル
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:13.44,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,触れていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:18.09,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,罰則なったとか 聞きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:23.50,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,論にほだされ論理捨て
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:28.75,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,理性なきリスクゲームなど 申請
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.86,0:24:36.66,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,稀代の痛いのを以って 光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:44.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,実際とアン実際とをミステイツク
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:53.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,一切の理解の向こうに So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.50,0:24:57.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.52,0:25:01.12,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.71,0:25:09.52,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TV-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前 世上的诸多星辰混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时人与神之间的界限还很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这 是个围绕一家之间的爱与重生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要凭自己活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规矩也要我们定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到麻烦 遇到新问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定要我们三人决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全归明惠 我才不干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要琴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想让她在我这吃闲饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的睡眠不足全都是拜他们所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去那个女人那里了 而是对琴上下其手…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上下个屁!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那种搓衣板就应该拿来洗衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 那不正好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 归你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个搓衣板可是很能吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可小心你那的妖怪别被吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于她的待遇 不是已经决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个也应该同意过的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可是但是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的议题就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我们自己 以及我们伟大的母亲之名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵守完美无缺的十戒!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这三人议会 不过只是形式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事情都是你一人决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩根本没有其他选项
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考虑的从来都是做出对我们最好的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 我的娃娃被冲走的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说可是最糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个小姑娘你争我抢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没必要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀~嗬~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是恶魔组织吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来打扰咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是恶魔啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真发达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是管理与运营镜都所有系统的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是穿水手服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不能容忍你随便挥舞兵器的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给老娘收起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对你的警告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才刚讲完!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做的真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手! 给我放回箱子里去!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿 吽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见你别拦我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋可越了雷池了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 消消气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然用魔法道具粉碎梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是魔法少女干的事儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我饶不了她!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在关注那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才不是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神社的实验室做的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我借你?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能还给我就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你挺通情达理的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见 后面就交给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿 吽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没带稍微弄一下就坏的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不希望你误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这上司有的只是纯粹的好奇心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们跟着嘛 就是以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为璞玉锤是有点特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是哪儿都能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里跟神社的实验室还真有点像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞研究的必需条件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都是一样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住持在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马大师?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们鞍马寺的最高负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是三人议会的议长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际全权掌管着这个都市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不太像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人议会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实也不是真正意义上的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正意义?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有明惠 和你们最接近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些缘由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话就长了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好像都很仰仗你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是人都无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事顺利就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计你已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是作为父母的代理治理着这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经治理了许久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是第一次有你这样的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次来到这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但好像只有老师他知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可真想 见一次你那位老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是个怪人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有机会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上我们和外界没有接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方是刻意造出的世外桃源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从孩提时代就一直在思考这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是回不去的话也很不方便的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要我的帮助 我随时乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也随时会帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 你要找的东西找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说黑色的兔子 我也有些头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不巧它现在不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能给你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的母亲就是父亲画出来的一只黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是屡见不鲜的偶然罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始你们就是三兄妹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很热闹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫你做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}哎呀 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就打得火热啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如来乃一世界无二能仁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求同类而不可得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若非领会佛法 无法从常见之物中有所得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛法之道以及心之相通自在难悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中无去亦无来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲说佛法 普度众生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 八濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪弄丢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你钻到地板下面的时候被勾住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢啦 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她满身的泥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都写了那么多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去都城玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有寺庙 有神社 有房屋 有许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时还有商贩开设的集市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要悄悄去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸不准我们去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便 咱们去踢球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去都城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是人类的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道看起来不像人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是看起来像人而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那群阴阳师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是露馅了确实很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去玩儿球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不像你 头脑简单四肢发达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是哥哥 脑子也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很有品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个子也很矮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很机灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有人的身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都城而已嘛 早晚总会去的吧
