Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后 你可以随便去都城啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是山上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你自己跟过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做得如你所愿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是还有什么需要的东西 就尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟之前让你受委屈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 虽然不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点自夸 不过我真是有个优秀的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马 你将来想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望终有一天 能去看看外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在此处之外的地方 证明我的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金刚巨人 毗舍丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.27,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：捏他自《铁人28号》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}「浮于世外的镜都 邪恶阴影试图扰乱城市平安」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}「恶影啊 吃我绝招」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}「利落冲拳!」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}「灭邪飞踢!」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞踢!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}「绝不能遗忘 那正义的遥控器…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了 不见了不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了不见了不见了不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西不见了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是遥控器啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情可好啊 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了 叫四神来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在找东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始搜索~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把操作系统装进去也就一样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以都跟你说要装个GPS了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不需要呢 又不可能会丢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 昨天白天的时候还在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天白天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别边吃边说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别撑着桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来点酱汁~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那三傻瓜交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是游戏控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是宅女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的遥控器在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净说些听不懂的胡话 脑子被敲了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个死假小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给我到家外面去玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}目前 鞍马寺正进行临时安全检查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是鞍马?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}请诸位配合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}目前 鞍马寺正进行临时安全检查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类住的地方一直都乱糟糟闹哄哄的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天似乎格外热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑童子!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多人一大早就在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马寺的人还真闲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看您说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们尊贵的八濑童子 是不是又在准备茶会呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一个内心和钱包都很充裕的家里蹲真好呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 你这只鸟!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞了 八濑童子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个路口左侧 马上无路可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的遥控器到底跑哪去啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 是三月食堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有哪有 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事想询问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢啦 辛苦啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是伏见 干得漂亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很了解你的 你可能干了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有哪有哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你怎么找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保密哦 不然她会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开喝 喝个痛快!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}遥控器 遥控器 遥控器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸亏装了GPS 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用多久 我们科学小组
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会和鞍马住持一起 向外面世界进发啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三个月亮…这里是哪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这里是外面世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又是大闹一场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为翔子太有趣了 结果我略有点得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个遥控器 是她来这里后做的第一个满载回忆的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 难得你说得这么感伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违地见到了前同僚 是不是勾起了思乡之情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫司的直属部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以根据对情况的判断 不受限制自由地行动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是捏一把汗的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你可以说是个逃兵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看您说的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我基本算是被人强行拉来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对那个璞玉锤的分析如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从各个方面说 博士真是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带来的技术也很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那孩子也说肯帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是要感谢神社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是您父母的女儿的可能性有多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那感觉 就像我在和父亲说话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那双眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我回忆起了许多过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他们有生我之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是再不快点回来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也快等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这看孩子的工作也做够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不远了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的夙愿 就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.70,0:25:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些东西 是绝对不舍得扔的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西 我有好~多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.42,0:25:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满载对妈妈的回忆的 最珍贵最珍贵的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.11,0:25:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍贵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.97,0:25:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍贵的…东西却…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.48,0:25:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 二女和了不起的妖怪们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.56,0:25:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆 是没有替代品的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.66,0:26:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
